","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Nicky Guadagni (born August 1, 1952) is a Canadian actress who has worked on stage, radio, film and television.","name":"Nicky Guadagni","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"尼基·瓜达尼（Nicky Guadagni，1952年8月1日-）是一位加拿大女演员，曾在舞台、广播、电影和电视领域工作。","name":"尼基·瓜达尼","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Никки Гуаданьи","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"尼基·瓜達尼（Nicky Guadagni，1952 年 8 月 1 日-）是一位加拿大女演員，曾在舞台、廣播、電影和電視領域工作。","name":"尼基·瓜達尼","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1109406_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1772691634022,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/boprqXZexBatujVC07gZzzxjWk.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":53,"name":"Phim Gây Cấn"},{"id":27,"name":"Phim Kinh Dị"}],"homepage":"","id":1109406,"imdb_id":"tt26744645","origin_country":["GB"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Compulsion","overview":"","popularity":3.3458,"poster_path":"/s3MzSdsMcmxmpVJMuH5ezNPjzs7.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":68755,"logo_path":null,"name":"Cork Films","origin_country":""},{"id":8464,"logo_path":null,"name":"Do Productions","origin_country":"ZA"},{"id":251012,"logo_path":null,"name":"Primal Empire Studios","origin_country":"GB"},{"id":14262,"logo_path":"/x04bvG6G7J3EfweMELPmTRnYwSL.png","name":"Templeheart Films","origin_country":"GB"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"GB","name":"United Kingdom"}],"release_date":"2024-11-10","revenue":0,"runtime":101,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Compulsion","video":false,"vote_average":6.016,"vote_count":31}},"person_33192_translations":{"at":1772691638077,"data":{"id":33192,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Joel Edgerton (born 23 June 1974) is an Australian actor, director, writer, and producer. He has appeared in the films Star Wars: Episode II – Attack of the Clones (2002), Star Wars: Episode III – Revenge of the Sith (2005), Warrior (2011), Zero Dark Thirty (2012), The Great Gatsby (2013), Black Mass (2015), Loving (2016), It Comes at Night (2017), and Red Sparrow (2018) and The King (2019).  In 2015, Edgerton received a nomination for the Directors Guild of America Award for Outstanding Directing – First-Time Feature Film for The Gift, a psychological horror-thriller film Edgerton wrote, directed, co-produced, and in which he co-starred. Edgerton garnered further critical acclaim for his performance as Richard Loving in the 2016 historical drama Loving, for which he received a nomination for the Golden Globe Award for Best Actor. In 2018, he wrote, directed and starred in the drama Boy Erased, about gay conversion therapy. In 2019, he starred and co-wrote The King.","name":"Joel Edgerton","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"💥Джоэл Эдгертон. Родился в 1974-ом году в Блэктауне, Австралия. Рос в семье со старшим братом. Отец работал юристом, а мать была медсестрой. Учился в Австралийской академии исполнительских искусств. Работает актёром, режиссёром и сценаристом. С 2018-го состоит в отношениях со стилисткой Кристин Сентенера, у пары 2 девочки-двойняшки, имена не раскрываются\n\n🎬Главные проекты🎬: «Воин» (2011), «Великий Гэтсби» (2013), «Тёмная материя» (2024), «Король Англии» (2019)\n\n⭐Интересный факт⭐: Джоэл много лет тренируется бразильским джиу-джитсу и регулярно участвует в соревнованиях","name":"Джоэл Эдгертон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Joel Edgerton wurde am 23. Juni 1974 in Blacktown, Australien, geboren. Nach der Schule besuchte er die Nepean Drama School und wurde in seinem Heimatland vor allem durch seine Darstellung des Will in der australische Fernsehserie The Secret Life of Us bekannt. 2001 brachte ihm diese Rolle eine Nominierung für den AFI Award ein.\n\nEdgertons internationaler Durchbruch folgte mit Star Wars: Episode II – Angriff der Klonkrieger, wo er Luke Skywalkers Onkel Owen spielte und auch in Star Wars: Episode III – Die Rache der Sith war er wieder zu sehen. Joels Bruder Nash Edgerton, auch Schauspieler, diente Ewan McGregor in beiden Filmen als Stuntman.\n\nNeben einigen Theaterproduktionen, wo Joel Edgerton King Henry in Henry V, Prince Hal in Henry III and spielte, trat der Schauspieler auch in weiteren Fernsehserien wie The Three Stooges, Dossa und Joe und Saturn’s Return mit.\n\nAußerdem ist Edgerton bekannt für sein Mitwirken bei Spielfilmen wie The Thing, Zero Dark Thirty und seine Darstellung des Tom Buchanan in Baz Luhrmanns Remake von Der große Gatsby, das 2013 in den Kinos läuft.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HU","iso_639_1":"hu","name":"Magyar","english_name":"Hungarian","data":{"biography":"Joel Edgerton 1974. június 23-án született Blacktownban, New South Walesben, Ausztráliában, Michael és Marianne Edgerton fiaként. Egy testvére van, Nash, aki szintén a filmiparban tevékenykedik.\n\nJoel 1991-ben végzett a The Hills Grammar Schoolban, majd a University of Western Sydneybe került, ahol a Nepean Drama Schoolban képezte magát tovább – innen egyenes útja vezetett a színházi produkciókig és a Sydney Teathre Companyig.\n\nEdgerton nevét először az ausztrál tévés sorozat, a The Secret Life of Us (2001) miatt ismerte meg a szélesebb közönség, majd olyan produkciókban kapott kiugrási lehetőséget, mint a Star Wars II. rész - A klónok támadása (2002) vagy a Star Wars III. rész – a Sithek bosszúja (2005).\n\nA Star Wars után egyre keresettebbé váló színész a következő években olyan filmekben szerepelt, mint a Ned Kelly - A törvényen kívüli (2003), az Artúr király (2004), a Mr. Tűsarok (2005) és a Suttogás (2007), de filmes karrierje miatt nem hanyagolta el a színpadot sem, és rendszeresen feltűnt mind ausztrál, mind amerikai színpadokon.\n\nOlyan kasszasikerekhez adta a nevét, mint  Az Őrzők legendája (2010) vagy a Warrior - A végső menet (2011) Tom Hardy oldalán, A dolog (2011), a Timothy Green különös élete (2012), az Oscar-díjas Zero Dark Thirty - A bin Láden-hajsza (2012) és A nagy Gatsby (2012) című remake.\n\nEdgertont legutóbb az Exodus: Istenek és királyok (2014) című Ridley Scott-filmben láthatjuk, ám 2015-ben is több filmjét mutatják majd be, illetve ő írta az Országúti bosszú (2014) című krimi történetét.\n\nA színész ismert emberszeretetéről és civil munkásságáról is, évek óta a The Fred HollowsFoundation egyik nagykövete.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Τζόελ Έτζερτον","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Urodził się w Blacktown w Nowej Południowej Walii jako młodszy syn Marianne Margarethe (von Dort) i Michaela Edgertona, prawnika / dewelopera[. Jego starszy brat Nash Edgerton jest filmowcem i kaskaderem. W 1991 ukończył The Hills Grammar School. Uczęszczał do szkoły teatralnej przy University of Western Sydney, zanim występował w różnych spektaklach, zwłaszcza w Sydney Theatre Company. Grał w Gwiezdnych wojnach: Część II - Atak klonów (2002), Królu Arturze (2004), Gwiezdnych wojnach: Część III - Zemsta Sithów (2005) i Wojowniku (2011) i Królu (2019).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"조엘 에저튼","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"喬爾·埃哲頓","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"乔尔·埃哲顿","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ジョエル・エドガートン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"ג'ואל אדגרטון","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BG","iso_639_1":"bg","name":"български език","english_name":"Bulgarian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джоел Едгертън","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"جويل إجيرتون","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BY","iso_639_1":"be","name":"беларуская мова","english_name":"Belarusian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джаэл Эдгертан","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RS","iso_639_1":"sr","name":"Srpski","english_name":"Serbian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Џоел Еџертон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джоел Еджертон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"ta","name":"தமிழ்","english_name":"Tamil","data":{"biography":"","name":"ஜோல் எட்கர்டன்","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"LV","iso_639_1":"lv","name":"Latviešu","english_name":"Latvian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Džoels Edžertons","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"جوئل ادگورتون","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"Joel Edgerton (narozen 23. června 1974) je australský herec, režisér, scenárista a producent. Objevil se ve filmech Star Wars: Epizoda II - Klony útočí (2002), Star Wars: Epizoda III - Pomsta Sithů (2005), Válečník (2011), 30 minut po půlnoci (2012), Velký Gatsby (2013),  Black Mass: Špinavá hra (2015), Lovingovi (2016), Přicházejí v noci (2017) a Rudá volavka (2018) a Král (2019).\n\nV roce 2015 získal Edgerton nominaci na cenu Directors Guild of America za vynikající režii - celovečerní debut za psychologický hororový thriller Dárek, který Edgerton napsal, režíroval, spoluprodukoval a v němž si zahrál jednu z hlavních rolí. Další uznání kritiky získal Edgerton za roli Richarda Lovinga v historickém dramatu Lovingovi z roku 2016, za kterou byl nominován na Zlatý glóbus za nejlepší mužský herecký výkon.\n\nV roce 2018 napsal scénář, režíroval a hrál v dramatu Vymazaný kluk o konverzní terapii homosexuálů. V roce 2019 si zahrál hlavní roli a podílel se na scénáři filmu Král.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"祖爾·艾哲頓","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"โจเอล เอดการ์ตัน","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1159559_keywords":{"at":1772691640576,"data":{"id":1159559,"keywords":[{"id":2546,"name":"mask"},{"id":310,"name":"artificial intelligence (a.i.)"},{"id":9663,"name":"sequel"},{"id":9826,"name":"murder"},{"id":10714,"name":"serial killer"},{"id":12339,"name":"slasher"},{"id":12570,"name":"whodunit"},{"id":17987,"name":"killing spree"},{"id":160612,"name":"self-referential"},{"id":161184,"name":"reboot"},{"id":177695,"name":"crime spree"},{"id":207046,"name":"murder mystery"},{"id":234025,"name":"masked villain"},{"id":234906,"name":"murder spree"},{"id":290395,"name":"casual"},{"id":309060,"name":"teen horror"}]}},"tv_285770_keywords":{"at":1772691641121,"data":{"id":285770,"results":[{"name":"romcom","id":9799},{"name":"romance","id":9840}]}},"person_42376_translations":{"at":1772691651156,"data":{"id":42376,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Zahn McClarnon is an American film and television actor of Native American and Irish descent. He's best known for his roles as Joe Leaphorn on AMC's series Dark Winds (in which he was also an executive producer), Big on Hulu's series Reservation Dogs, Yvon on NatGeo's miniseries Barkskins, Tulimak in the film Togo, Crow Daddy in Doctor Sleep, Hallett in the film Braven, Toshaway in AMC's The Son, The Professor in the film Bone Tomahawk, Akecheta on Westworld, Hanzee Dent on the series Fargo, Officer Mathias on A&E's Longmire, Running Fox on TNT's miniseries Into the West, and Little Big Man in the film Crazy Horse.","name":"Zahn McClarnon","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Зан Маккларнон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"扎恩·迈克拉农","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"זאהן מקלרנון","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"沙恩·麥卡隆林","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Зан Маккларнон","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ซาห์น แม็กคลาร์นอน","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"扎恩·麥克拉農","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"زان مک‌کلارنون","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"잔 매클라넌","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"زان مكلارنون","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HY","iso_639_1":"hy","name":"","english_name":"Armenian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Զան ՄակՔլարնոն","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ザーン・マクラーノン","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ζαν ΜακΚλάρνον","primary":false}}]}},"person_2178031_translations":{"at":1772691659030,"data":{"id":2178031,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Liu Guanlin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"刘冠麟，1981年12月19日出生于黑龙江，毕业于北京舞蹈学院音乐剧系。  2005年，参演电视剧《大汉天子3》，饰演季擒虎。 2008年3月，加盟了宁财神自编自导的12集古装剧《龙虎山客栈》。2011年1月，出演张纪中执导的古装动作戏《菊花醉》 。2013年，刘冠麟加盟了宁财神执导的古装职场轻喜剧《龙门镖局》 。2014年，与秦海璐、胡冰共同主演都市时尚情感作品《妈妈向前冲》  。同年参演电视剧《十月围城》。","name":"刘冠麟","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Liu Guanlin","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"류관린","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lưu Quán Lân","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"劉冠麟，1981 年 12 月 19 日出生於黑龍江，畢業於北京舞蹈學院音樂劇系。\n\n2005 年，參演電視劇《大漢天子 3》，飾演季擒虎。\n\n2008 年 3 月，加盟了寧財神自編自導的 12 集古裝劇《龍虎山客棧》。2011 年 1 月，出演張紀中執導的古裝動作戲《菊花醉》 。2013 年，劉冠麟加盟了寧財神執導的古裝職場輕喜劇《龍門鏢局》 。2014 年，與秦海璐、胡冰共同主演都市時尚情感作品《媽媽向前衝》 。同年參演電視劇《十月圍城》。","name":"劉冠麟","primary":false}}]}},"person_1175961_translations":{"at":1772691659524,"data":{"id":1175961,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"John Tang Yat-Kwan was born on 24 October 1976. He is an actor, known for Yesteryou, Yesterme, Yesterday, The True Hero","name":"John Tang Yat-Kwan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"邓一君（John Tang Yat Kwan，1976年10月24日－），前香港童星及演员，九岁时经老师介绍于香港电台教育电视开始演出，曾参与多出电影及电视剧。他曾凭1994年《记得...香蕉成熟时》内杨醒波一角，获提名香港电影金像奖最佳新演员奖。\n\n2005年退出娱乐圈，于宏利金融担任专业理财顾问，其后获擢升为高级分行经理及考取CFP认可财务策划师专业资格。于2006年结婚，育有一女邓颂情（Kristen）。","name":"邓一君","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"鄧一君，前香港演員，九歲時經聖若瑟小學音樂老師介紹於香港電台教育電視開始演出，曾參與多齣電影及電視劇。他曾憑 1994 年《記得. . . 香蕉成熟時》內楊醒波一角，獲提名角逐香港電影金像獎最佳新演員獎。\n\n2005 年退出娛樂圈，其後考取 CFP 認可財務策劃師專業資格，現擔任財富管理公司總監。","name":"鄧一君","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Đặng Nhất Quân","primary":false}}]}},"tv_271548_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1772691672658,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/gTPfMUXFIgG6HZeR5hif2fvGzOv.jpg","created_by":[{"id":1584305,"credit_id":"67117d578e844657b7fad79b","name":"Cem Karcı","original_name":"Cem Karcı","gender":2,"profile_path":null}],"episode_run_time":[150],"first_air_date":"2024-11-13","genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"}],"homepage":"https://www.startv.com.tr/dizi/sahipsizler","id":271548,"in_production":false,"languages":["tr"],"last_air_date":"2026-02-25","last_episode_to_air":{"id":6948067,"name":"Episode 23","overview":"","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"air_date":"2026-03-04","episode_number":23,"episode_type":"finale","production_code":"","runtime":137,"season_number":2,"show_id":271548,"still_path":"/rgNufBgtAoZmw4IWZoZtCfOsDkx.jpg"},"name":"Sahipsizler","next_episode_to_air":null,"networks":[{"id":778,"logo_path":"/qWvC2SCqIGhm7hPGtqaPjL4tPvx.png","name":"Star TV","